    "description": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Golden Erinys Stance]</p>\n<p>You can make fury's fang unarmed attacks. These deal 1d6 piercing damage; are in the brawling group; and have the agile, backstabber, finesse, forceful, nonlethal, and unarmed traits.</p>\n<p>While in the stance, if you critically hit with a melee Strike that deals piercing damage, the target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} (with a DC to remove equal to your class DC); this is in addition to any critical specialization effect you might gain from the attack.</p>",
