    "actionType": null,
    "description": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Kaiju Stance]</p>\n<p>You become Large and are clumsy 1. The only Strikes you can make are shattering earth attacks. These strikes deal 1d8 bludgeoning damage, are in the brawling group, and have the backswing, fatal d12, reach, and unarmed traits. On a critical success with a shattering earth attack, all creatures other than you that are within 10 feet of the target, including the target itself, take 1 point of bludgeoning splash damage per weapon damage die.</p>\n<p>You ignore difficult terrain.</p>",
