    "actionType": null,
    "description": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Lunging Stance]</p>\n<p>You can use Reactive Strike against a creature that is outside your reach but within the reach you would have with a Lunge. If you do, you increase your range with the Strike by 5 feet.</p>",
