    "actions": null,
    "actionType": null,
    "description": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Multishot Stance].</p>\n<p>While you are in this stance, your penalty for Double Shot is reduced to -1, or -2 if you add the extra action to make three Strikes. If you move from your position, this stance ends.</p>",
