    "actionType": null,
    "description": "<p>You and your allies in your kinetic aura gain resistance 5 to bludgeoning and piercing damage. In addition, you and your affected allies roll flat checks to recover from persistent damage twice and take the higher result; this is a fortune effect.</p><hr /><p><strong>Level (+4)</strong> The resistance increases by 2.</p>",
