    "actionType": null,
    "description": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Peafowl Stance]</p>\n<p>The only Strikes you can make are melee Strikes with the required sword. Once per round, after you hit with a monk sword Strike, you can Step as a free action as your next action.</p>",
